thread.title: RED DUST IN THE ROUTE 466

title: RED DUST IN THE ROUTE 466
text:
Only registered TrekEarth members may write critiques. Photographer's Note 
This is a pasture in the same area of the previous photo. This time we can see a part of the route 466, not paved, between Borrazópolis city and Porto Ubá in the banks of Ivaí River. Temos aqui a mesma pastagem da foto anterior, mas aqui podemos ver um trecho não pavimentado da BR 466 que vai de Borrazópolis até Porto Ubá, nas barrancas do Rio Ivaí. 
Nobody has marked this note useful
